# Project Structure

- `scripts/rna_seq/`
  - pairwise RNA-seq differential expression scripts
  - Q4 all-cell RNA clustering script
- `scripts/atac_seq/`
  - pairwise ATAC-seq differential accessibility script
  - Q8 all-cell ATAC clustering script
- `data/rna_seq/`
  - ScriptSeq RNA-seq input tables
- `data/atac_seq/`
  - ATAC-seq bigBed peak files
- `results/deseq2/` and `results/limma_voom/`
  - pairwise RNA-seq outputs
- `results/atac_seq/`
  - pairwise ATAC-seq outputs
- `results/clustering/`
  - Q4 and Q8 all-cell clustering outputs
- `results/summary/`
  - report-ready RNA summary tables and text

Root-level `*.R` files are lightweight wrappers that preserve the old entry points.
